GateDocument.TextWithNodes: It came from Liverpool, that was the port base to the Titanic, destroyed by God because of the arrogant insult of captain Smith (also from Liverpool): " Not even God can sink my ship " (not only the captain, but also the rest of the crew and even the orchestra playing at the Titanic were from Liverpool).
